  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Basically, I was staying at home, learning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With my father.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was studying some Hebrew words, the letters of the Hebrew alphabet, basic mathematics-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning was some school in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, I think that this disappear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was question of less than half year, in which I, of course, I was included there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, we were studying practically how to, to write and read the local language.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bulgarian and Hebrew letters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At home, we were speaking Bulgarian language.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, my grandparents were speaking some kind of, for me, unknown language that I tried to understand and communicate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, I, I were able to understand the meaning of some words.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this language was called Ladino, which is the-- actually, this language that the Spanish Jews, the Jews that came from Spain, used to speak between them and--",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, resemble very much to the older Spain, older Latin language, perhaps from-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for this reason, the semantics of this language remain in the name of the language, Ladino, which is Latin language.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this was the language that also my parents were speaking between themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't study formally this language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But how happen usually because of the curiosity of the little children, anytime when they hear something, some language that is spoken by the parents, they start almost intuitively to learn and understand.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this, perhaps, later on helped me when I was in my own traveling in the world very quickly absorbed other languages, specially with Latin roots.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But of course, the official language to us a Bulgarian language, which they spoke on a very academic level, a very high literary level.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
